{
  "stem": "150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I say that, you know, they weren't killing us, which they really weren't, other than the beatings that would kill you eventually, they killed us when they felt there was a reason for it.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the one that I do remember was when three guys whose boots had worn out and it was winter time, and they took a blanket from a dead man and cut it into strips and wrapped it around their feet and to go to work.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Germans called that sabotage, you know, destroying German property, so they hanged them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the rest of us have to stand there for an extra hour and watch them being hanged, and then watch them dangle in the wind.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, it was very cold and windy that day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know, so just don't fool around with German property.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the work went on and then a very-- again, a very interesting, a very unusual thing happened, which again, sort of makes you wonder about human nature, or does God have a sense of humor, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a man in the camp who, in the ghetto, had risen to a rather high position within the hierarchy because the main thing that we were doing in the ghetto in Lithuania was building an airfield for the German Air Force.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all of us-- the 10,000 or so-- were working with that particular project.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this man, whose name was Phillip Berkman-- and who before the war, was a salesman of-- advertising salesman for a small German language newspaper in Lithuania-- rose to be the leader of the brigade, and eventually, the leader of the whole project, or part of the project.",
      "word_count": 48
    }
  ],
